FBIS3-38055 "drsov039_a_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Embassy Adviser Lysenko Expelled From United States LD2502213294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 2052 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502213294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Igor Borisenko] [Excerpts] Washington, 25 Feb -- The U.S. State Department has just declared pesona non grata Aleksandr Iosifovich Lysenko, adviser of the Embassy of the Russian Federation in Washington. [passage omitted] Aleksandr Lysenko arrived in Washington in July 1993. Under the instructions of the State Department he is obliged to leave the territory of the USA within seven days.
